---
title: Sicilian-Style Salmon & Panzanella Salad with Roast Potatoes & Chargrilled Capscium Relish
description: You're going to love this one – the aroma of the butter sauce against the succulent salmon is mind-blowingly good. With roasted potatoes, plus creamy goat cheese and crispy croutons in the Panzanella salad, we reckon it's destined for greatness!
